\begin_layout Standard
The Elko County Information Operations Policy Manual (maintained as the master 
\shape italic
Policy_Manual.lyx
\shape default
 file) is the 
\series bold
designated Authoritative System of Record for all governance controls
\series default
,
 including the departmental security and service management standards defined herein.
 It establishes the mandatory frameworks required to ensure consistency,
 accountability,
 and compliance with applicable laws,
 regulations,
 and industry standards across the County's technology landscape.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
Executive Summary
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The policies contained herein are 
\series bold
administratively mandatory
\series default
 and align the Department’s strategic objectives with statutory requirements and industry control frameworks.
\end_layout

